22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fcannes-market-the-desperate-chase-sales-finecut-1235999645%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fcannes-market-the-desperate-chase-sales-finecut-1235999645%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Country%20Has%20A%20256-Kilometre%20Highway%20That%20Never%20Bends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia's%20Highway%2010%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20world's%20longest%20straight%20road%2C%20surpassing%20Australia's%20Eyre%20Highway%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post.%3C%2Fem%3E%20This%20revelation%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20the%20realm%20of%20transportation%20infrastructure%2C%20as%20the%20expansive%20stretch%20of%20Highway%2010%20extends%20farther%20than%20its%20predecessor%2C%20offering%20travellers%20a%20remarkable%20journey%20across%20vast%20distances%20with%20unobstructed%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fmagazines%2Fpost-magazine%2Ftravel%2Farticle%2F3232243%2Fworlds-most-famous-road-and-highest-longest-most-dangerous-straightest-and-curviest%5C%22%3E256-kilometre%20(159-mile)%20asphalt%20ruler%3C%2Fa%3E%20cuts%20through%20the%20vast%20Rub%20Al-Khali%20desert%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Empty%20Quarter%2C%20the%20largest%20sand%20desert%20in%20the%20world.%20Originally%20built%20as%20a%20private%20road%20for%20King%20Fahd%2C%20Highway%2010%20offers%20a%20unique%20driving%20experience-one%20devoid%20of%20turns%20for%20a%20staggering%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arabnews.com%2Fnode%2F1263776%2Foffbeat%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EArab%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20confirms%20the%20impressive%20stretch%2C%20highlighting%20that%20it%20runs%20from%20Haradh%2C%20a%20city%20known%20for%20its%20oil%20and%20gas%20reserves%2C%20to%20Al%20Batha%2C%20near%20the%20border%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fworld-records%2F62919-longest-straight-road%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Eit%20cuts%20through%20the%20desert%20with%20no%20bends%20left%20or%20right%20or%20any%20appreciable%20gradient%20up%20or%20down.%20The%20super-straight%20stretch%20has%20an%20estimated%20driving%20time%20of%20around%202%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20Eyre%20Highway%2C%20a%20146-kilometre-long%20stretch%20connecting%20Western%20Australia%20and%20South%20Australia%2C%20held%20the%20record%20for%20the%20straightest%20road.%20While%20driving%20on%20Highway%2010%20might%20seem%20like%20setting%20the%20cruise%20control%20on%20autopilot%2C%20drivers%20are%20warned%20against%20complacency.%20Information%20found%20on%20dangerousroads.org%20emphasises%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20lack%20of%20bends%2C%20collisions%20are%20not%20uncommon.%20The%20desert%20landscape%20presents%20its%20own%20set%20of%20hazards%2C%20with%20vehicles%20needing%20to%20be%20cautious%20of%20stray%20camels%20and%20the%20occasional%20kangaroo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20reasons%20behind%20building%20such%20a%20long%2C%20straight%20road%20remain%20unknown%2C%20some%20speculate%20it%20served%20as%20a%20high-speed%20route%20for%20the%20King.%20Regardless%20of%20its%20origin%2C%20Highway%2010%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20modern%20engineering%20and%20a%20truly%20unique%20driving%20experience%2C%20albeit%20one%20that%20requires%20a%20healthy%20dose%20of%20driver%20awareness.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715757480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsks8bpo_saudi-arabias-highway-10_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhighway-10-saudi-arabia-this-country-has-a-256-kilometer-highway-that-never-bends-5667445%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20highway%2C%20whic