A%22Who%20Was%20Colonel%20Waibhav%20Anil%20Kale%2C%20Ex-Indian%20Army%20Officer%20Killed%20In%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EColonel%C2%A0Waibhav%C2%A0Anil%20Kale%20(Retd)%2C%20the%20Indian%20national%20who%20was%20working%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20(UN)%20as%20a%20security%20service%20coordinator%2C%20was%20killed%20after%20the%20vehicle%20he%20was%20travelling%20in%20came%20under%20attack%20in%20Gaza's%20Rafah%20region.%20Colonel%C2%A0Kale's%20killing%20marks%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-indian-army-officer-col-waibhav-anil-kale-working-with-un-killed-in-gaza-attack-5660940%C2%A0%2520%C2%A0%C2%A0%5C%22%3EUN's%20first%20international%20casualty%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20began%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20and%20Israel%20have%20both%20called%20for%20investigations%20into%20the%20incident.%20Colonel%C2%A0Kale%2C%20who%20retired%20from%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%202022%2C%20is%20survived%20by%20his%20wife%20Amruta%20and%20two%20teenage%20children%2C%20son%20Vedant%20and%20daughter%20Radhika.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EHere%20are%20some%20facts%20about%20Colonel%C2%A0Waibhav%C2%A0Anil%20Kale%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Colonel%C2%A0Waibhav%C2%A0Anil%20Kale%2C%2046%2C%20spent%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20the%20armed%20forces.%20He%20came%20from%20a%20family%20dedicated%20to%20military%20service%2C%20with%20his%20brother%2C%20Group%20Captain%20Vishal%20Kale%2C%20serving%20in%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%2C%20his%20cousin%C2%A0Colonel%C2%A0Amey%20Kale%C2%A0in%C2%A0the%C2%A0army%2C%20and%20his%20brother-in-law%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20Prasant%20Karde%20(Retd).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Colonel%C2%A0Kale%C2%A0was%20from%20Nagpur%C2%A0and%C2%A0he%C2%A0studied%20at%20the%20Somalwar%C2%A0high%20school.%20He%20later%20got%20a%20BA%C2%A0degree%C2%A0in%20Humanities%20from%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%C2%A0University%2C%C2%A0before%20getting%20a%20Diploma%20of%20Education%20in%20Senior%20Defense%20Management%20from%20Devi%20Ahilya%20Vishwavidyalaya%2C%20Indore%2C%20as%20per%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fwaibhav-anil-kale-627396220%2Fdetails%2Feducation%2F%C2%A0%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20In%202009%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20Certificate%20Program%C2%A0in%20International%20Humanitarian%20Law%C2%A0from%20the%20International%20Red%20Cross.%C2%A0In%202012%2C%20he%20finished%20another%20Certificate%20Program%20in%20Behavioural%20Science%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20National%20Integration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Colonel%C2%A0Waibhav%C2%A0Anil%20Kale%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Army%20in%201998.%20He%20commanded%20the%2011%20JAK%20Rifles%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20served%20as%20an%20instructor%20at%20the%C2%A0army's%C2%A0Infantry%20School%20in%20Mhow%2C%20operated%20in%20the%20northeast%20and%20the%20Siachen%20glacier%2C%20and%20actively%20engaged%20in%20counterintelligence%20and%20counterterrorism%20operations.%20He%20held%20various%20positions%2C%20including%20Battalion%20Commander%20and%20Rifle%20Company%20Commander%2C%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20Col%C2%A0Kale%C2%A0retired%20from%20the%C2%A0Army%C2%A0permanently%20in%202022.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%C2%A0While%20in%C2%A0the%20Army%2C%20Colonel%C2%A0Kale%20served%20as%20a%20Contingent%20Chief%20Security%20Officer%20with%20the%20United%20Nations%20from%202009%20to%202010.%20Just%205-6%20weeks%20ago%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20UNDSS%2C%20this%20time%20as%20a%20Security%20Coordination%20Officer%2C%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715753100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F0s6nfil8_colwaibhavanil-kale-linkedin_625x300_15_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-col-waibhav-anil-kale-ex-indian-army-officer-killed-in-gaza-5666604%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Colonel%20Waibhav%20Anil%20Kale%20(Retd)%