ias%20(procession%20of%20Muslim%20mourners%20on%20Muharram)%2C%20there%20are%20regular%20roadblocks%20to%20taking%20out%20immersion%20processions%20on%20Durga%20Puja%20and%20Kali%20Puja.%20Should%20this%20be%20allowed%20to%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20slammed%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20for%20spurning%20the%20invite%20to%20the%20'Pran%20Pratishtha'%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDespite%20receiving%20a%20formal%20invitation%2C%20she%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20inauguration%20ceremony%20(at%20the%20Ram%20temple)%20to%20appease%20a%20certain%20vote%20bank.%20You%20(people)%20are%20not%20her%20vote%20bank%2C%20the%20infiltrators%20are.%20She%20is%20scared%20of%20rubbing%20her%20vote%20bank%20the%20wrong%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20accusing%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20spreading%20falsehoods%20over%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20he%20said%20she%20was%20'misleading'%20people%20on%20the%20central%20legislation%20that%20is%20aimed%20at%20granting%20asylum%20and%20permanent%20residency%20to%20immigrant%20minority%20settlers%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20is%20misleading%20the%20people%20saying%20the%20CAA%20could%20invite%20trouble%20for%20the%20people.%20I%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20all%20that%20the%20legislation%20is%20not%20aimed%20at%20bringing%20any%20harm%20to%20anyone.%20All%20bonafide%20citizens%20can%20go%20on%20leading%20their%20lives%20here%20with%20dignity.%20No%20power%20in%20the%20world%20can%20stop%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Jain%20refugees%20from%20becoming%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20ruling%20TMC%20was%20trying%20to%20turn%20infiltrators%20into%20Indian%20citizens%20while%20coming%20out%20in%20Opposition%20to%20the%20CAA%2C%20which%20is%20aimed%20at%20granting%20permanent%20residency%20to%20oppressed%20minorities%2C%20including%20the%20Matuas%20who%20crossed%20over%20from%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20remind%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20that%20the%20central%20government%2C%20and%20not%20state%20governments%2C%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20grant%20citizenship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssuring%20that%20the%20Matua%20community%2C%20which%20inhabits%20Bongaon%20and%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20would%20be%20able%20to%20avail%20rights%20under%20the%20CAA%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BFour%20phases%20of%20polling%20have%20been%20completed.%20The%20elections%20to%20380%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20including%2018%20in%20Bengal%2C%20are%20done%20and%20dusted.%20I%20can%20tell%20you%20today%2C%20that%20of%20the%20380%20seats%20for%20which%20polling%20has%20already%20happened%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20secured%20absolute%20majority%2C%20winning%20270%20seats.%20The%20battle%20for%20us%20now%20is%20to%20cross%20400-plus%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarning%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20that%20those%20involved%20in%20'scams'%20wouldn't%20be%20spared%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20'cut%20money'%20culture%20to%20infiltration%2C%20from%20bomb%20blasts%20to%20Bhatija's%20(CM's%20nephew%20Abhishek%20Banerjee)%20goons%20harassing%20people%2C%20from%20'Syndicate%20Raj'%20to%20utter%20lawlessness%2C%20Bengal%20is%20staring%20at%20a%20state%20of%20complete%20lawlessness.%20Only%20Narendra%20Modi-Ji%20can%20save%20the%20state%20from%20plunging%20further%20into%20the%20abyss.%20Those%20involved%20in%20the%20chit%20fund%20scam%2C%20teacher%20recruitment%20scam%2C%20municipal%20recruitment%20scam%2C%20ration%20scam%2C%20cow%20and%20coal%20smuggling%20should%20be%20ready%20to%20go%20to%20jail.%20No%20one%20will%20be%20spared.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20was%20campaigning%20for%20BJP%20candidate%20Shantanu%20Thakur%2C%20