n%20if%20an%20ancient%20society%20could%20have%20survived%20for%20a%20million%20years%2C%20it%20should%20have%20been%20able%20to%20colonise%20and%20explore%20the%20whole%20Milky%20Way%20galaxy.%20He%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20they%20haven't%2C%20so%20why%20not%3F%20I%20think%20the%20answer%20might%20be%2C%20probably%2C%20is%20that%20that%20civilisation%20is%20precarious%2C%20and%20rare.%20And%20that%20we%20should%20really%20think%20of%20human%20civilization%20as%20being%20like%20a%20tiny%20candle%20in%20a%20vast%20darkness.%20And%20we%20should%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20ensure%20that%20that%20candle%20does%20not%20go%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715748600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Felbr9jfg_elon-musk_625x300_29_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdont-see-any-evidence-elon-musk-asserts-aliens-never-visited-earth-5666570%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20said%20that%20there%20are%20thousands%20of%20broadband%20spacecraft%20that%20SpaceX%20operates%20in%20low%20Earth%20orbit%2C%20however%2C%20he%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20evidence%20of%20either%20extraterrestrial%20life%20or%20UFOs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdont-see-any-evidence-elon-musk-asserts-aliens-never-visited-earth-5666570%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdont-see-any-evidence-elon-musk-asserts-aliens-never-visited-earth-5666570%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdont-see-any-evidence-elon-musk-asserts-aliens-never-visited-earth-5666570%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Biggest%20mistake%20was...'%3A%20Kaif%20criticizes%20Rahul's%20captaincy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715748481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-110135731%2Ci