egin%20in%20October.%20The%20airport%20will%20be%20linked%20by%20six%20roads%20and%20a%20rapid%20rail-cum-metro%2C%20besides%20pod%20taxis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Noida%20airport%20is%20billed%20to%20be%20the%20largest%20in%20India%20upon%20completion%2C%20and%20the%20third%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20after%20Delhi%20airport%20and%20Hindon%20airbase%20in%20Ghaziabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2031-km%20greenfield%20expressway%20is%20being%20built%20to%20connect%20the%20airport%20to%20the%20Delhi-Mumbai%20Expressway%20at%20Ballabhgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Highway%20Authority%20of%20India%20(NHAI)%20is%20also%20constructing%20a%20750-metre%20eight-lane%20road%20to%20connect%20the%20expressway%20with%20the%20airport%2C%20said%20Yamuna%20Expressway%20Industrial%20Development%20Authority%20(YEIDA)%20CEO%20Arun%20Vir%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20of%20the%20lanes%20are%20likely%20to%20open%20by%20June%2015%20while%20the%20rest%20four%20may%20become%20operational%20by%20August%2015%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20three%20other%20airport%20connectivity%20projects%20have%20also%20been%20awarded%20to%20the%20NHAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%208.2-km%20long%20and%2030-metre%20wide%20road%20is%20being%20built%20towards%20the%20north%20and%20east%20of%20the%20airport%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2063%20crore%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20ready%20in%20eight%20months%2C%20said%20Mr%20Singh.%20This%20road%20will%20connect%20the%20airport%20cargo%20terminal%20with%20the%20Yamuna%20Expressway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20VIP%20access%20road%20will%20also%20be%20built%20to%20reach%20the%20Noida%20Airport%20from%20the%20Yamuna%20Expressway%2C%20said%20the%20YEIDA%20boss.%20This%20will%20be%20used%20by%20VIPs%20and%20during%20emergencies%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Detailed%20Project%20Report%20(DPR)%20of%20the%20Rapid%20Rail-cum-Metro%20Rail%20has%20been%20approved%20and%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20government%20