mf-chief-2024-05-13%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20a%20tsunami.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20very%20little%20time%20to%20get%20people%20ready%20for%20it%2C%20businesses%20ready%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20bring%20tremendous%20increase%20in%20productivity%20if%20we%20manage%20it%20well%2C%20but%20it%20can%20also%20lead%20to%20more%20misinformation%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20more%20inequality%20in%20our%20society.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Georgieva%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chatgpt-jobs-layoffs-kristalina-georgieva-world-economic-forum-davos-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esounded%20warning%20calls%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20AI.%20In%20January%2C%20she%20penned%20a%20blog%20post%20where%20she%20predicted%20that%20AI%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FBlogs%2FArticles%2F2024%2F01%2F14%2Fai-will-transform-the-global-economy-lets-make-sure-it-benefits-humanity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewill%20affect%20almost%2040%25%20of%20jobs%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRoughly%20half%20the%20exposed%20jobs%20may%20benefit%20from%20AI%20integration%2C%20enhancing%20productivity.%20For%20the%20other%20half%2C%20AI%20applications%20may%20execute%20key%20tasks%20currently%20performed%20by%20humans%2C%20which%20could%20lower%20labor%20demand%2C%20leading%20to%20lower%20wages%20and%20reduced%20hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20Georgieva%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20most%20extreme%20cases%2C%20some%20of%20these%20jobs%20may%20disappear%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20IMF%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGeorgieva's%20warnings%20appear%20to%20be%20prescient%2C%20considering%20the%20new%20offerings%20that%20have%20been%20served%20up%20by%20AI%20upstarts%20like%20OpenAI%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20OpenAI%20announced%20its%20latest%20flagship%20AI%20model%2C%20GPT-4o.%20The%20model%2C%20which%20will%20be%20made%20free%20to%20all%20users%2C%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fhello-gpt-4o%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecan%20reason%20across%20audio%2C%20vision%2C%20and%20text%20in%20real%20time%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20making%20it%20suitable%20for%20tasks%20like%20teaching%20and%20translation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-most-impressive-gpt-4o-demo-videos-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemos%20of%20the%20software%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20taken%20the%20internet%20by%20storm%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchat-gpt4o-not-killing-jobs-teaching-translation-customer-service-experts-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereigniting%20concerns%20that%20AI%20could%20decimate%20the%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20we%20know%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20OpenAI's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20has%20regularly%20warned%20people%20of%20AI's%20potential%20impact%20on%20the%20job%20market.%20On%20May%207%2C%20Altman%20told%20attendees%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.brookings.edu%2Fevents%2Fshifting-geopolitics-in-the-age-of-ai-a-conversation-with-sam-altman%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBrookings%20Institution%20panel%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20people%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-says-ais-economic-impact-top-concern-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderestimating%20AI's%20impact%20on%20the%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGPT-%204%20didn't%20have%20this%20huge%20detectable%20impact%20on%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20so%20people%20were%20kind%20of%20like%2C%20'Oh%20well%2C%20we%20were%20too%20worried%20about%20that%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20a%20problem%2C'%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%2C%20referencing%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopenai.com%2Findex%2Fgpt-4%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20model%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20OpenAI%20released%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20fear%20that%20we%20just%20won't%20take%20that%20one%20seriously%20enough%20going%20forward%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20massive%2C%20massive%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20some%20experts%20do%20believe%20that%20the%20AI's%20rise%20will%20provide%20job%20seekers%20with%20different%20opportunities%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20LinkedIn%20vice%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-degrees-less-important-as-ai-spreads-linkedin-vp-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAnnesh%20Raman%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20podcast%20interview%20that%20while%20AI%20will%20reduce%20the%20value%20of%20technical%20skills%2C%20it%20will%20also%20make%20soft%20skills%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%201980s%2C%20when%20Microsoft%20released%20Excel%2C%20people%20were%20petrified%20and%20said%20it%20would%20put%20all%20of%20these%20accountants%20out%20of%20a%20job.%20We've%20got%20more%20accountants%20now%20than%20in%20the%201980s%2C%26quot%3B%20Simon%20Lucey%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Adelaide's%20Australian%20Institute%20for%20Machine%20Learning%2C%20told%20BI%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimf-chief-ai-revolution-striking-job-market-like-a-tsunami-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715745356000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6644188af27898f532d7b350%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimf-chief-ai-revolution-striking-job-market-