2Fgoogle-io-2024-live-updates-ai-search-android-announcements-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%2FO%3C%2Fa%3E%20conference%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20keynote%2C%20journalists%20were%20herded%20over%20to%20a%20demo%20area%20for%20Project%20Astra.%20It's%20an%20experimental%20effort%20to%20reimagine%20what%20AI%20agents%20can%20be%20in%20the%20future.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20always%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20universal%20agent%20that%20will%20be%20useful%20in%20everyday%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Google%20DeepMind%20chief%20Demis%20Hassabis%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20at%20the%20test%20location%2C%20Google%20let%20four%3Cspan%3E%20journalists%20at%20a%20time%20into%20little%20demo%20booths.%20Before%20we%20went%20in%2C%20while%20waiting%20in%20line%2C%20two%20members%20of%20the%20Project%20Astra%20team%20from%20DeepMind%20walked%20us%20through%20how%20to%20use%20the%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20described%20four%20modes%20for%20us%20to%20try%20out%3A%20Storyteller%2C%20Pictionary%2C%20Free-Form%20and%20Alliteration.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da8137ba-91b0-4c66-98c8-afa864214416%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EFree-Form%20mode%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20tried%20Free-Form%20mode.%20Max%20Cherney%2C%20a%20journalist%20from%20Reuters%2C%20held%20up%20a%20Google-provided%20Android%20phone%20and%20pointed%20the%20camera%20at%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BDescribe%20his%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20Max%20said.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%20model%20reviewed%20the%20phone's%20live%20video%20and%20said%20I%20was%20wearing%20casual%20clothes.%20An%20accurate%2C%20solid%20answer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20started%20dancing%20and%20Max%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20is%20he%20doing%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20responded%20incorrectly%2C%20kind%20of.%20It%20said%20I%20had%20put%20on%20sunglasses.%20Which%20was%20true%2C%20because%20I'd%20put%20on%20some%20sunnies%20to%20dance.%20But%20it%20didn't%20spot%20the%20dancing.%20Admittedly%2C%20I%20was%20dancing%20badly%2C%20so%20maybe%20the%20AI%20model%20gets%20a%20pass%20on%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246b71491-fcb9-46c7-88a9-863d36161877%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20stock%20quotes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%20Max%20asked%20Gemini%20to%20critique%20my%20attire%2C%20because%20he%20wanted%20Gemini%20to%20do%20some%20analysis%20and%20share%20a%20point%20of%20view.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20AI%20model%20said%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20provide%20stock%20quotes%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%20We%20all%20stopped%20as%20the%20AI%20magic%20had%20abruptly%20ended.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250804134-5575-4c26-8b42-8b85028b0e7d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20car%20and%20a%20story%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20then%20moved%20to%20a%20large%20touch%20screen%20that%20offered%20the%20four%20modes%20to%20try.%20I%20chose%20Pictionary.%20I%20drew%20a%20really%20bad%20car%2C%20and%20Gemini%20said%20%26quot%3Bthat%20looks%20like%20a%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20asked%20it%20to%20put%20the%20vehicle%20in%20an%20interesting%20story.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sleek%2C%20blue%20car%20sped%20down%20the%20highway%2C%20a%20lonely%20traveler%20on%20a%20moonlit%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20had%20the%20car%20drive%20into%20a%20marketplace%20and%20Gemini%20said%20doing%20that%20would%20be%20unsafe%20in%20reality%2C%20but%20it%20could%20make%20a%20good%20story%20plot%20twist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BIs%20that%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Gemini%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20drew%20a%20table%20of%20fruit%20at%20the%20market.%20It%20was%20even%20worse%20than%20the%20car.%20Then%20I%20said%20someone%