ee%20ingredients%20on%20the%20back%20are%20the%20ones%20in%20most%20quantities.%20If%20the%20main%20ingredient%20of%20your%20ice%20cream%20is%20water%20and%20not%20milk%2C%20and%20has%20over%2010%20percent%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fsearch%3Fq%3Dvegetable%2Boil%252C%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bidnia%26rlz%3D1C1RXQR_enIN1032IN1032%26oq%3Dvegetable%2Boil%252C%2Bthe%2Bbetter%2Bidnia%2B%26gs_lcrp%3DEgZjaHJvbWUyBggAEEUYOdIBCTMwMzlqMGoxNagCCLACAQ%26sourceid%3Dchrome%26ie%3DUTF-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evegetable%20oil%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20then%20it%20is%20NOT%20ice%20cream%20but%20a%20frozen%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6tFka-Br4-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6tFka-Br4-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6tFka-Br4-%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20(%40thebetterindia)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20FSSAI%2C%20ice%20cream%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F215034%2Fmillet-dessert-recipes-chocolate-cake-healthy-vegan-pudding-laddu-laddoo-lifestyle-tan42%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilk-based%20dessert%3C%2Fa%3E.%20FDA%20too%2C%20mandates%20that%20a%20true%20ice%20cream%20must%20have%20at%20least%2010%20percent%20milk%20in%20it.%20So%20if%20the%20label%20does%20say%20milk%2C%20it%20is%20NOT%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20frozen%20desserts%20may%20taste%20and%20feel%20similar%20to%20ice%20creams%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%20to%20know%20that%20frozen%20desserts%20have%20a%20higher%20fat%20content.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20bad%20cholesterol%2C%20and%20cause%20heart%20diseases.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3EHealthSite.com%20report%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20(hydrogenated%20oils)%20are%20banned%20for%20US%20foods%2C%20with%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO)%20calling%20for%20a%20total%20ban%20worldwide%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20you%20know%20how%20to%20check%20if%20your%20ice%20cream%20is%20fake%2C%20make%20it%20a%20thumb%20rule%20to%20check%20the%20ingredient%20list%20before%20indulging%20in%20your%20favourite%20summer%20staple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349789%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Frozen%20desserts%20are%20masquerading%20as%20ice%20creams%20in%20the%20market.%20How%20do%20you%20differentiate%20between%20them%3F%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20simple%20steps%20to%20identify%20real%20ice%20creams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349789%2Fhow-to-identity-real-ice-cream-vs-frozen-dessert-fssai-guidelines-read-label%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IFS%20Officer%20Is%20On%20a%20Mission%20to%20Save%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Endangered%20Plants%3B%20What%20Makes%20them%20Special%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20dusk%20sets%2C%20anyone%20who%20stops%20by%20the%20research%20wing%20of%20the%20forest%20department%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Haldwani%20looking%20for%20IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%2C%20won%E2%80%99t%20find%20him%20there.%20Instead%2C%20the%20officer%20can%20be%20found%20promenading%20through%20the%20centre%E2%80%99s%20campus%20which%20teems%20with%20abundant%20flowering%20plants%20and%20fruit%20trees.%20The%20sight%20of%20a%20glorious%20green%20carpet%20thriving%20at%20a%20height%20of%20300%20ft%20above%20sea%20level%20is%20baffling.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F163949%2Fjakkur-bengaluru-lake-pollution-cleaning-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Especies%20of%20flora%3C%2Fa%3E%20do%20you%20think%20reside%20within%20this%2025-acre%20land%3F%20Take%20a%20guess.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20850%20species%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20reveals%20Chaturvedi.%20In%20this%20forest-like%20ecosystem%20that%20he%20has%20spent%20the%20last%20few%20years%20cultivating%2C%20bamboo%20and%20cactus%20befriend%20each%20other%2C%20while%20crickets%2C%20butterflies%20and%20insects%20stop%20by%20to%20pay%20their%20respects%20to%20the%20honeysuckle.%20The%20air%20is%20crisp%20and%20the%20walk%20is%20therapeutic%20for%20Chaturvedi%2C%20who%20pauses%20to%20put%20his%20experience%20into%20words%3B%20then%20proceeds%20to%20say%20that%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20do%20justice.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20most%20taken%20aback%20by%20Chaturvedi%E2%80%99s%20optimistic%20view%20are%20the%20naysayers