ough%20these%20globetrotters%20hailed%20from%20different%20industries%2C%20they%20shared%20a%20common%20thread%20%E2%80%94%20they%20all%20had%20farming%20backgrounds.%20So%20after%20working%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20four%20professionals%20quit%20their%20cushy%20jobs%20and%20returned%20to%20their%20hometowns%20%E2%80%94%20Prabu%20and%20Arun%20to%20Trichy%3B%20Shashidhar%20and%20Bhargav%20to%20Hyderabad%20%E2%80%94%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20then%20pooled%20their%20diverse%20experiences%20in%20hotel%20management%2C%20food%20science%2C%20marketing%20and%20finance%2C%20and%20brainstormed%20ideas%20to%20use%20their%20farmland%20as%20a%20valuable%20resource%20to%20build%20a%20thriving%20food%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPassionate%20about%20building%20sustainable%20food%20systems%2C%20they%20zeroed%20in%20on%20growing%20India%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20supergrains%20%E2%80%94%20millets.%20Known%20for%20its%20drought-resistant%20qualities%20and%20nutritional%20benefits%2C%20millet%20seemed%20like%20the%20perfect%20candidate%20to%20promote%20both%20health%20and%20sustainability.%20Their%20efforts%20gave%20birth%20to%20%E2%80%98Siri%20Millets%E2%80%99%20in%202017%20with%20a%20mission%20to%20popularise%20the%20grain%20through%20value-added%20products%20like%20snacks%2C%20flakes%2C%20vermicelli%2C%20pasta%2C%20and%20much%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20as%20they%20were%20about%20to%20launch%20their%20products%20on%20a%20grand%20scale%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20dealt%20a%20significant%20blow%20to%20their%20meticulously%20planned%20strategies.%20Yet%2C%20this%20adversity%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20hidden%20blessing%2C%20spurring%20them%20to%20innovate.%20Out%20of%20this%20challenge%20emerged%20the%20idea%20of%20millet-based%20ice%20cream!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20path%20was%20not%20easy%2C%20yet%20they%20persisted%20with%20research%20and%20development%20for%20eight%20months.%20Finally%2C%20their%20labour%20of%20love%2C%20