m%3Echai%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eparatha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(an%20Indian%20flatbread)%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20already%20be%20planning%20our%20lunch%20menu.%20During%20lunch%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20plan%20for%20evening%20snacks%20and%20while%20having%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewe%E2%80%99d%20discuss%20dinner%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20on%20Sundays%2C%20the%20menu%20was%20non-negotiable.%20The%20spot%20on%20the%20table%20was%20reserved%20for%20%3Cem%3Emutton%20biryani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20dish%20comprising%20meat%20cooked%20in%20spices%2C%20herbs%20and%20yoghurt%2C%20served%20with%20rice).%20And%20as%20the%20family%20gathered%20to%20feast%2C%20bonds%20were%20formed%2C%20laughs%20were%20shared%2C%20jokes%20were%20cracked%2C%20and%20memories%20were%20etched%20onto%20a%20young%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5hXwn_SsBe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5hXwn_SsBe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5hXwn_SsBe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Sumeet%20Saigal%20(%40sumeetsaigal__)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20professional%20years%20saw%20her%20pursue%20a%20degree%20in%20hotel%20management%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20MBA%20in%20tourism%20management%20in%20Australia.%20Corporate%20life%20took%20a%20front%20seat%20for%20years%2C%20but%20as%20she%20maintains%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20took%20my%20finger%20out%20of%20the%20food%20pie.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHarnessing%20a%20forte%20for%20spice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEveryone%20in%20the%20MasterChef%20kitchen%20is%20familiar%20with%20Saigal%E2%80%99s%20reverence%20for%20spices.%20She%20insists%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348080%2Fhow-to-make-masala-powder-spice-mix-at-home-recipes-mdh-everest-sambar-biryani-pav-bhaji-masala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflavouring%20condiments%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20instead%20powerful%20symbols%20of%20Indian%20gastronomy%3B%20the%20ingredients%20that%20render%20Indian%20food%20its%20distinct%20taste.%20%E2%80%9CSpices%20are%20our%20superpower%2C%20something%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20double%20guess.%20Like%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20rainbow%2C%20each%20spice%20is%20beautiful%20in%20its%20own%20right.%20I%20see%20them%20like%20music%20notes.%20You%20can%20adjust%20the%20levels%20but%20still%20end%20up%20with%20a%20beautiful%20rendition%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20apt%20example%20of%20this%20metaphor%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20dabba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(spice%20box)%20in%20Indian%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20each%20have%20the%20same%20dabba%20but%20a%20curry%20in%20my%20house%20won%E2%80%99t%20resemble%20the%20one%20in%20yours.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20amazing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20to%20further%20pay%20homage%20to%20Indian%20spices%2C%20Saigal%20shares%20a%20dream%20she%20has%20long%20since%20harboured%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%98Sauce%20Boss%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20platform%20that%20will%20make%20sauces%20easily%20available%20and%20accessible%20for%20people%20in%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20experiences%20that%20influenced%20this%20dream%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20my%20trips%20to%20India%2C%20I%20see%20a%20huge%20variety.%20A%20curry%20in%20North%20India%20is%20different%20from%20one%20in%20South%20India%3B%20a%20curry%20in%20Kolkata%20is%20different%20from%20one%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20on%20the%20western%20coast.%20While%20we%20recognise%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F348165%2Fcurry-map-of-india-rogan-josh-kadhi-lal-maas-jholi-masor-tenga-besara-pulissery-gushtaba%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepth%20of%20flavour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20popular%20opinion%20is%20that%20a%20curry%20is%20complex%20with%20over%2050%20ingredients.%20Through%20Sauce%20Boss%2C%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20out%20the%20versatility%20of%20Indian%20food%2C%20where%20one%20sauce%20can%20be%20used%20to%20make%20a%20range%20of%20dishes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6Gf27Dr8Ah%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6Gf27Dr8Ah%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv