ne%20month%20and%20provides%20all%20the%20necessary%20information%2C%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20which%20the%20teacher%20learnt%20over%20his%20three%20years%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20distribute%20my%20knowledge%20and%20create%20awareness%20that%20such%20a%20technique%20exists.%20The%20beauty%20is%20that%20it%20requires%20minimum%20water.%20The%20system%20consists%20of%20PVC%20pipes%20which%20supply%20nutrient-rich%20water%20solution%20directly%20to%20the%20roots%20of%20the%20plant.%20This%20water%20is%20then%20rotated%20and%20reused.%20Plants%20get%20nutrition%20through%20the%20water%20used%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20he%20has%20trained%20over%205%2C000%20people.%20Over%20time%2C%20Rasik%20felt%20the%20need%20to%20provide%20this%20information%20to%20more%20people%20for%20free%2C%20and%20started%20the%20Maruti%20Nandan%20Charitable%20Trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20conduct%20a%20mega%20city%20awareness%20campaign%2C%20and%20reach%20more%20people.%20It%E2%80%99s%20essential%20that%20people%20learn%20this%20technique%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20saves%20water%20and%20needs%20no%20soil.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20always%20wanted%20to%20serve%20people%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20path%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rasik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20limited%20availability%20of%20arable%20land%2C%20hydroponics%20is%20a%20great%20option%20to%20fulfil%20the%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20judiciously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20support%20Rasik%E2%80%99s%20mission%20to%20promote%20a%20sustainable%20alternative%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347133%2Fplant-nursery-business-after-quitting-job-bhausaheb-navale-sharad-patil-greens-and-blooms-pune-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etr